{"tid":2387021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"GameStop大戰網民大勝 做空基金Citron認輸 宣佈再也不會發表做空報告","createTime":"2021-01-30T04:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T04:14:22.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b71f03447ecbb7372492e71d2707857426f7976d","tid":2387021,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"知名空頭香櫞：未來不再發布做空報告 將專注於長期投資<br />\n<br />\n近期華爾街不斷上演逼空行情，散戶攻勢猛烈之際，知名做空機構香櫞研究 (Citron Research) 突然宣布不再發布做空報告，未來將改為散戶投資人尋找做多的長期投資機會。<br />\n<br />\n香櫞研究創辦人 Andrew Left 周五 (29 日) 透過 Youtube 影片宣布，即日起，香櫞將結束長達 20 年的做空研究，不再發布做空報告，目標轉向為散戶投資人尋找長期投資機會。<br />\n<br />\nLeft 表示：「20 多年前，我創立香櫞的目的是為了保護個人免受華爾街、詐欺行為和股票促銷的衝擊，創辦香櫞的初衷應在於對抗體制，但實際上我們卻成為其中一員。」<br />\n<br />\n香櫞上周表示，GameStop(GME-US) 股價只值 20 美元，不會再漲下去，並稱買入該股的買家為牌桌上的受騙者。<br />\n<br />\n上述言論引發鄉民不滿，隨即引爆後續的瘋狂逼空，將 GameStop 股價自原先的 40 美元，最高推升至超過 400 美元，迫使多家看淡該股的對沖基金平倉認虧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4564325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4564325&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=41bae3ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4564325</a>"},{"pid":"f455d7c279a6d1d0982f11f8714ec27322bf0537","tid":2387021,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9ABUKq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9ABUKq.png&h=640fe319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStronghold大法贏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbf2a4c7352c40bb796bd26dc91e99ca32e0806","tid":2387021,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8gUGp0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F